Description: NetCtl Command-Line Interface
 Command-line tools for managing NetCtl network control daemon.

Package: netctl-dashboard
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, netctl (>= ${source:Version})
Description: NetCtl Web Dashboard
 Web-based dashboard for monitoring and managing the NetCtl daemon.
 Provides real-time network visualization, flow tracking, and configuration.
